summary: A medium sized house with a Dwemer theme.
descriptionHtml:
1.1 update includes mannequins, weapons racks and weapon plaques.

When updating remember to remove ALL GEAR from the house or it WILL BE thrown into Lord Sheogorath's cupboard to never see the light of day again.

Medium sized house comes with everything you would expect from a house mod such as a blacksmith area, alchemy area, enchanting area and of course containers to store all your loot!

The house is navmeshed with the exception of the cave area which wouldn't play nice with followers no matter how hard I tried to get it to work.

No DLC required.

Please note this is my first mod so if you come across any problems please let me know! And feedback is always appreciated.
